name: Magnolia Center Church of Christ
review_text: It's been awhile and kind of new to Southern California as we're from Northern California ...just came for 10days and 2-3 years later...Hard to meet people especially during COVID. Pandemic all about over and found this church very close to residence. I went and so very glad I did. I met more caring honest good people that visit than the entire 2-3years here. The church is fantastic.
